# Stock File Format
Although similar, this format is very different from headlines.html. Below are line definitions for these files.

These files are pretty much colon-separated CSV lines with custom headers and line breaks.

Title=MyStock | REQUIRED
Section=MyPortfolio | REQUIRED
DATA=SYMBOL;Symbol Name;Last Price;Change;High;Low;Open;Volume;52Week High;52 Week Low;

Sep0: Symbol (Col 00) - Can be arbitrary - Limit = 31
Sep1: Name (Col 10) - Can be arbitrary - Limit = 31
Sep2: Last Price (Col 01)
Sep3: Change (Col 02)
Sep4: High (Col 04)
Sep5: Low (Col 05)
Sep6: Open (Col 06)
Sep7: Volume (Col 07)
Sep8: 52High (Col 08)
Sep9: 52Low (Col 09)
